data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Midway! This meticulously updated gem on a .40-acre lot offers new flooring, a spacious sunroom, and an outdoor screened-in porch. Inside, find 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a split floor plan for added privacy. Entertain in the large living room, separate dining area, and breakfast nook. Outside, enjoy the fenced backyard and space for your camper/RV. Conveniently located to Ft. Stewart, shopping, and I-95. With a newer septic tank and appliances, don't miss your chance - Sold as is.
